de.topicmapslab.tmql4j.query
Interface IQuery

All Known Implementing Classes:
QueryImpl, Tmql4OntopiaQuery, TMQLQuery, TMQLQuery
public interface IQuery

Interface definition of a query, which can be handled by the TMQL4 engine or a plug-in. Each implementation of this interface represent a query of a specific language.

Author:
Sven Krosse
